<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Meqenet Credit Limit Has Been Updated</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .highlight {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4CAF50;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Meqenet</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Your Credit Limit Has Been Updated</h2>
      <p>Dear Customer,</p>
      <p>We're pleased to inform you that your Meqenet credit limit has been updated.</p>
      <p>Your new credit limit is <span class="highlight">{{newLimit}} ETB</span>.</p>
      <p>Previous credit limit: {{oldLimit}} ETB</p>
      <p>You can use your available credit for purchases with any of our partner merchants.</p>
      <p>To view your current credit status, please log in to your Meqenet app.</p>
      <p>Thank you for choosing Meqenet!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The Meqenet Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at {{supportEmail}} or call {{supportPhone}}.</p>
      <p>&copy; {{year}} Meqenet. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>